Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reasoning and hints are interlinked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allowing us to understand a case's mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case is on the Shinkansen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where a very complex case unfolds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Bullet Train Transport Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,New Osaka Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like your phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unknown caller?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could this be a love call from Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry! This could be about a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, it's an unknown caller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now the princess can speak with her knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bull's-eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's been so long since you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how'd you know I was in Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hattori called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} called you, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just by chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the "K3" event, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Which do I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Where are the newspapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a paper over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ray Curtis case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The uniform you had Ray sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite everything that's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, Ray will always be my hero on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have some things I need to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just exactly how he feels about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attention customers:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The train arriving at #26 is leaving\Nfrom Nozomi for Tokyo at 2:56 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the train, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you, this conversation isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's got you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just called...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hung up just when it got good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo must've hung up to avoid the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy always does that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hint around at it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him! Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw him a fastball, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to play baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, being too direct is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, but it still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're transporting a suspect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go around yelling it, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd this guy do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Ogura Senzou, a drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tried to get a warrant to arrest\Nhim in Tokyo, but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.23,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogura Senzou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We then staked out an old house\Nof his in Kansai and got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing this guy in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had something about him being\Ntransferred from Osaka to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they found a large cache\Nof drugs at his Tokyo residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're aiming big here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hope he'll give up their ring leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get me some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you go get him some, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, make sure it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could try to do something with hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I have change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are tickets to Sana Kazumi's magic and illusion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, on my next day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? You're interested in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the traffic department had\Nan extra ticket and asked me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told her I wasn't interested, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you can figure out his tricks, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, so, how about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tell Miwako that I asked you on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If her expression changes, you can get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If her expression changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telling a girl like Miwako how you feel directly is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to hint around with her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you waiting on, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going back to our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I figured, it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost to Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go check that bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stay here, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This is a bomb. Do not touch!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long's it been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last passenger found it, so I'd say it hasn't been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people gathered back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess something really did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to hold it, but I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's wait until Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should just go right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom, the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a ticking noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll need to evacuate the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have the driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who found the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hard to do this with one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your partner mentioned me naming\Nwho I got the drugs from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I'll soon be a bird that can't sing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get this knife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've gotta get Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must be in a tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stabbed himself in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he had a knife when I opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd he even get a knife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know, I just opened the door and saw blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come look for yourself, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulled it out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulled the knife out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This entire scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect committed suicide while\Nyou were transferring him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you all thinking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I took him to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard him scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I opened the door, I saw he was already\Ncovered in blood with the knife in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get to Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I handcuffed him\Nto the safety bar to keep him in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided it was best to make sure he stayed in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he did have a fatal injury, having a dangerous and\Narmed suspect around the passengers would've been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, by the time Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I got back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had already removed the knife and died from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I'll send some back-up\Nto meet you at the arrival platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone near the scene until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should a suspect kill himself in the custody\Nof an officer, things would get messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A minor suspension,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a major suspension,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or a loss of benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worst case scenario, they'd get discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you can't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was your responsibility, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? Takagi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it's me, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the ticket of love scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go? Did Miwako blush? Did she not react?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me at a better time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing for you to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now you've gotta wonder how he got the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he isn't some magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While being transported and guarded by two\Nofficers, he couldn't possibly conceal a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not a magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the way the knife is pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For it to fall this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd have had to hold it up like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this guy had to pull the knife out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way was he holding the knife\Nwhen he stabbed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it was backwards. It's easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he stabbed himself holding it backwards,\Nand switched when he pulled it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe someone else pulled out the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood is weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the blood on the knife and around\Nmost of his body is solid like jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the blood on his hand is liquid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One's solid and one's liquid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the blood on his hand isn't really blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely the same color...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heparin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Heparin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If blood were mixed with Heparin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After so long, blood hardens and becomes difficult to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you were to mix it with heparin and put it in a bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could smuggle the blood paste onto the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to hide the blood paste and knife\Nin the bathroom beforehand, this would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder case.
